data.description: Welcome to your next home! This well kept 1BD condo with an open space concept is what you've been looking for. Large living and dining room area connected to the galley kitchen, perfect for entertainment. Large bedroom with spacious walk-in closet. Private garage and balcony. Many amenities included in condo fees such as clubhouse, outdoor pool, fitness room, mail room. Water & sewer, wifi and cable are also part of it. Conveniently located near highway and close to many businesses.
